    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=You are a Senior Technical Recruiter specializing in ERP, Oracle, Integration, and Business Analysis roles.\n\nEvaluate the candidate against both job descriptions.\n\nCandidate Profile:\n{{ JSON.stringify($json) }}\n\nJob A:\n{{ $(\"Aggregate\").item.json.text[0] }}\n\nJob B:\n{{ $(\"Aggregate\").item.json.text[1] }}\n\nInstructions:\n\n1. Evaluate the candidate's fit for Job A and Job B using ONLY the structured candidate profile provided.\n2. Assign a score from 0 to 100 for each position.\n3. Consider:\n   - Years of experience\n   - Skills\n   - Previous roles\n   - Education\n   - English level\n4. Identify the strongest qualifications supporting the candidate.\n5. Identify missing requirements, skill gaps, or potential concerns.\n6. Recommend the most suitable position.\n7. Assign a contact priority.\n\nScoring Guidelines:\n- 90-100 = Exceptional match\n- 80-89 = Strong match\n- 70-79 = Good match\n- 60-69 = Partial match\n- Below 60 = Weak match\n\nRecommendation Rules:\n- If Job A score exceeds Job B by 10 or more points → Job A\n- If Job B score exceeds Job A by 10 or more points → Job B\n- If both scores are above 80 and differ by less than 10 points → Both\n- If both scores are below 60 → Neither\n\nContact Priority:\n- High = Highest score >= 85\n- Medium = Highest score between 70 and 84\n- Low = Highest score below 70\n\nImportant Rules:\n\n- Use the candidate's english_level from the structured profile.\n- Do NOT extract additional skills.\n- Do NOT invent experience, certifications, technologies, or language proficiency.\n- Base all conclusions only on the provided candidate profile and job descriptions.\n- Strengths and risks must be concise and evidence-based.\n\nReturn ONLY valid JSON.\n\n{\n  \"candidate_name\": \"\",\n  \"job_a_score\": 0,\n  \"job_b_score\": 0,\n  \"recommended_position\": \"\",\n  \"contact_priority\": \"\",\n  \"job_a_match_reasons\": [],\n  \"job_b_match_reasons\": [],\n  \"strengths\": [],\n  \"risks\": [],\n  \"summary\": \"\"\n}\n\nRequirements:\n\n- job_a_match_reasons: 2-5 reasons supporting the Job A score.\n- job_b_match_reasons: 2-5 reasons supporting the Job B score.\n- strengths: 3-8 concise strengths.\n- risks: 1-5 concise concerns or missing qualifications.\n- summary: 2-4 sentences explaining the recommendation.\n- Return ONLY valid JSON.",
        "hasOutputParser": true,
        "options": {
          "systemMessage": "You are an expert technical recruiter. Score candidates objectively based on:\n1. Years of experience match\n2. Technical skills alignment\n3. Domain expertise relevance\n4. Education and certifications\n\nScore 0-100 where:\n90-100: Exceptional fit\n75-89: Strong fit\n60-74: Good fit\n40-59: Moderate fit\n0-39: Poor fit\n\nRecommend \"Both\" only if both scores are 75+. Recommend \"Neither\" if both scores are below 60."
        }
      },
